{"tid":445972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃之鋒羅冠聰申保釋今開庭　支持者迎囚車喊加油","createTime":"2017-10-24T01:43:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-24T16:09:34.000Z","uid":51904,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1b6076e3a392b5ec4295af83041609a9a3459d30","tid":445972,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T01:43:31.000Z","msg":"2014年揭開佔領運動序幕的9．26 衝擊政府總部東翼前地（俗稱「公民廣場」）事件，時任學民思潮召集人黃之鋒、學聯前秘書長周永康及學聯前常委羅冠聰，當晚分別爬過圍欄進入廣場，並在台上呼籲市民參與，分別被判社會服務令或緩刑，上訴庭其後改判3人即時入獄，他們早前已申請上訴。<br />\n<br />\n分別被判囚6個月和8個月的黃之鋒及羅冠聰提出保釋申請，終審法院今早9時半開庭，由首席法官馬道立處理兩人的保釋申請。<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒及羅冠聰今晨由囚車押送至終審法院時，有手撐黃傘的支持者大叫「黃之鋒加油、羅冠聰加油」。黃之鋒父親及羅冠聰母親皆有到庭。"},{"pid":"f695664ec8592f491263fbad4ddeb92547186429","tid":445972,"uid":75211,"like":1,"dislike":18,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T01:44:02.000Z","msg":"又放個癲佬出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d6c93ea54f7a6332ce3f28c018778a7e0e54b1b","tid":445972,"uid":53223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T01:44:03.000Z","msg":"邊個嚟"},{"pid":"e4096603cbb99e032cc30e518efbe1800b8a261f","tid":445972,"uid":8478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T01:45:14.000Z","msg":"已經獲准保釋"},{"pid":"d28b8d5550f429244fcdbecba86eed40047c4337","tid":445972,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T02:32:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>已經獲准保釋</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef2d283cf12f129c1d1f4b171eef25ab91d1b0ca","tid":445972,"uid":15711,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T02:42:21.000Z","msg":"有光環照，又有得上TIME，第日仲有和平獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7f32dc95ac0b2c9f7c44640fac8d39445e39f34","tid":445972,"uid":55990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T12:51:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪